headline: American Made: Why NNN REIT Might Be a Better Choice Than Realty Income
summary: Realty Income is a giant net lease REIT with a diversified global portfolio.  NNN REIT is a modestly sized, U.S.-focused net lease REIT that specializes on the retail sector.  NNN REIT is small enough to benefit from its tight retailer relationships.
